sentences.en: 95% of our students are out-of-state students.
sentences.cn: 我们学生中的95%是外州的。

sentences.en: Out-of-state visitors are our bread and butter.
sentences.cn: 外省游客是我们的主要经济来源。

sentences.en: Another state like Delaware that allows out-of-state shareholders to set up companies.
sentences.cn: 另外一个像特拉华州的地方，允许其他州的股东建立公司。
